{"tid":1096944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夏天來臨係惡夢既開始","createTime":"2019-04-08T05:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:56:47.000Z","uid":227032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82189093b902671ed9b3eba4e04317118543d619","tid":1096944,"uid":227032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"天氣熱就唔洗講<br />\n仲要焗住，聞住堆臭汗味迫狗鐵番放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚訓覺又多蚊，屌你老母係要臨訓著先出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘都係喪開冷氣令到電氣費升幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都係中意香港所謂既&lsquo;冬天&rsquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴絲們係prefer夏天定冬天呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d895fb3e9bb35635c23eb68d1682e5ff349eb962","tid":1096944,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"夏天有嘢睇<br />\n冬天冇咁臭<br />\n都係選冬天算<br />\n唔想個鼻受罪"},{"pid":"4875f1a8692406c6be6e479b2dd7b16753f36fe7","tid":1096944,"uid":45219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"701a2ce6bf88ef6d0ecaa70e6031096836b9d2f6","tid":1096944,"uid":45219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"你講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}